{"name":"The Thetis","size":"gargantuan","type":"Vehicle","tag":"(80ft. by 20ft.)","alignment":"","hitDice":"9","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"15","speed":"0","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":true,"hpText":"--","speedDesc":"(water) 45 ft.; 15 ft. while sailing into the wind; 60 ft. while sailing with the wind","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"7","conPoints":"17","intPoints":"0","wisPoints":"0","chaPoints":"0","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside aboard the _Thetis_, [MON] commands the crew of the _Thetis_. [MON] gains one crew action which they can use only at the end of another creature's turn. [MON] regains spent crew actions at the start of its turn.","lairDescriptionEnd":"At full strength, the _Thetis_ has 15 crew members with the following stats in-combat: AC 13, HP 25. (+3 to checks/saves).\n\n_Actions:_\n\n> Shortsword: _Melee weapon attack_ +5 to hit, [1d6+3] slashing damage\n> Rifle: _Ranged weapon attack_ +5 to hit, [3d6] piercing damage","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the centaur's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the centaur's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the centaur dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Hull","desc":"**Armor Class** 15, **Hit Points** 300 (damage threshold 15)"},{"name":"Helm","desc":"**Armor Class** 18, **Hit Points** 50\n\nMove up to the speed of one of the ship's sails, with one 90-degree turn. If the helm is destroyed, the ship can't turn."},{"name":"Cannons","desc":"**Armor Class** 15, **Hit Points** 100\n\n_Ranged Weapon Attack_: +5 to hit, range 200/800 ft., one target. Hit: 27 (5d10) bludgeoning damage."},{"name":"Sails","desc":"**Armor Class** 12, **Hit Points 100**\n\n-5 ft. speed per 25 damage taken"}],"actions":[{"name":"Crewed","desc":"On its turn, the ship can take 2 actions, choosing from the options below. It can't take these actions if it has fewer than three crew.\n\n**Fire Cannon** The ship can fire its Cannon\n**Move** The ship can use its helm to move with its sails."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"poison","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"},{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"deafened"},{"name":"exhaustion"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"incapacitated"},{"name":"paralyzed"},{"name":"poisoned"},{"name":"prone"},{"name":"stunned"},{"name":"unconscious"}],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":0,"damage":[]}